data.description: Welcome to a spacious beautiful home nestled in a cul-de-sac! This residence boasts 5 bedrooms plus a bonus room in the lower level, perfect for creating your ideal home office or exercise area. The backyard is your personal paradise with mature trees providing shade, a brick paver patio for summer gatherings, an in-ground pool for refreshing dips, and updated decks for even more outdoor enjoyment. Inside, you'll discover the timeless elegance of mahogany hardwood floors in the living room, dining room, and hallway leading to the bedrooms. The owner's suite is generously sized, including a walk-in closet, and a private bathroom. The kitchen is equipped with newer stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample pantry space for all your culinary needs. In the lower-level family room, a fireplace provides warmth and comfort during the winter months. This home has been well maintained, with all windows replaced within the last five years, a new sump pump installed in 2023, added insulation in the attic (2022) for energy efficiency, upgraded electrical breakers (2022), a newer water heater (2020) and more.  Minutes from expressways, shopping malls, restaurants, entertainment, nearby park, and golf course. Don't miss the chance to make this property your own! Contact your Agent today to schedule a showing!
